// ZDoom supports a special XHAIRS lump that can be used to add custom 
// crosshairs to the choices under "Crosshair" in the Display Options menu.

// Crosshair number is the number that corresponds to the number in the lump 
// name of the crosshair graphic.

// https://zdoom.org/w/index.php?title=XHAIRS

1 "Cross 1"
2 "Cross 2"
3 "X"
4 "Circle"
5 "Angle"
6 "Triangle"
7 "Dot"